x+2x^2+3x^3+4x^4+...+nx^n = \frac{nx^{n+2}-(n+1)x^{n+1}+x}{(x-1)^2}
\sum_{n=1}^n nx^n = n\sum_{n=1}^n x^n
\sum_{n=1}^n x^n = \frac{x(x^n-1)}{(x-1)}
\therefore n\sum_{n=1}^n x^n = n(\frac{x(x^n-1)}{(x-1)})
\sum_{n=1}^n nx^n = n\sum_{n=1}^n x^n
S=x+2x^2+3x^3+4x^4+...+nx^n \ \ \ \ (1)
x\cdot S=x^2+2x^3+3x^4+4x^5+...+nx^{n+1}\  \ \ \ (2)
(1)-(2)\implies S(1-x)=x+x^2+\cdots+x^n-nx^{n+1}
x+x^2+\cdots+x^n=x\frac{x^n-1}{x-1}
x + 2x^2 + 3x^3 + 4x^4+...+nx^n
x-1
(x + 2x^2 + 3x^3 + 4x^4+...+nx^n)(x-1) = x(x + 2x^2 + 3x^3 + 4x^4+...+nx^n) - (x + 2x^2 + 3x^3 + 4x^4+...+nx^n)
nx^{n+1}
(n+1)x^{n+1}
-x^{n-1}
nx^{n+1} - x^{n-1} -...-x^2 - x
x-1
(nx^{n+1} - x^{n-1} -...-x^2 - x)(x-1) = nx^{n+1}(n-1) - (x^{n-1} +...-x^2 + x)(x-1)
x^n - x
nx^{n+2} - nx^{n-1} - x^n + x = nx^{n+2} - (n+1)x^{n+1} + x
\frac{1}{(x-1)^2} - 1
\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}} = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \binom{n+k}{n}x^n
1 + x + x^2 + x^3 + x^4+... = \frac{1}{x-1}
1 + x + x^2 + x^3+...+x^{n-1} = \frac{x^n - 1}{x-1}
